# NOBA Clinic — site root configuration
#
# The homepage file is named "lumiere-clinic.html" (kept as-is because
# admin.html and blog.html link back to it by that exact name, e.g.
# "lumiere-clinic.html#about", "lumiere-clinic.html#contact", ...).
# This line tells Apache to serve it when a visitor requests "/" or
# "https://nobaclinic.com" — exactly like a normal index.html would be
# served — without renaming the file or touching any internal links.
DirectoryIndex lumiere-clinic.html index.html
